Bob,

If you are referring to a Type 4 motor...

Most VW style carbs will fit on a Type 4 motor if you get the right castings
from CB Performance, EMPI, etc
So, Empi, Solex and Dellorto are all useable.
I would use Dellortos, no bigger than 36mm on a stock type 4.

Jon Stiles

